      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.TestExtractor<T>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.TestExtractor-1.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">An in-memory extractor for use in tests, examples, and benchmarks.\nYields items from either an <xref href=\"System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> or an\n<xref href=\"System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>, depending on which constructor is used.</p>\n"
