      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.TestLoader<T>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.TestLoader-1.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A simple in-memory loader for use in tests, examples, and benchmarks.\nIterates all items from the source stream and, when constructed with\n<code>collectItems: true</code>, makes them available via <xref href=\"Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.TestLoader%601.GetCollectedItems\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>\nafter the load completes.</p>\n"
