      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.Xunit.ManualProgressTimer",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.Xunit.ManualProgressTimer.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A controllable implementation of <xref href=\"Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IProgressTimer\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> for use in unit tests.\nFires <xref href=\"Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IProgressTimer.Elapsed\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> synchronously on demand via <xref href=\"Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.Xunit.ManualProgressTimer.Fire\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>,\nrather than on a background thread-pool thread after a real time interval.</p>\n"
    },
