      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.Xunit.SynchronousProgress<T>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.Xunit.SynchronousProgress-1.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">An <xref href=\"System.IProgress%601\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> implementation that invokes its callback synchronously\non the calling thread, rather than posting to a synchronisation context.</p>\n"
